1
00:01:32,010 --> 00:01:34,850
<i>LOVE AND REDEMPTION</i>

2
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:37,640
<i>EPISODE 2</i>

3
00:02:02,080 --> 00:02:04,940
Xuan Ji!

4
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:14,528
This is bad! There’s an intruder
in the secret ground!

5
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:35,138
Xuan Ji!

6
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:41,075
Who are you?

7
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:45,100
Xuan Ji!

8
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:54,140
Silver Snake!

9
00:02:58,120 --> 00:03:00,279
My mask!

10
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:02,340
Little Stammer, don’t go there!
Do you have a death wish?

11
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:41,620
Master, the entrance has been sealed.

12
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:46,440
Senior Heng Yang.

13
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:49,479
Junior, you’re back.

14
00:03:49,480 --> 00:03:52,839
The protective barrier was
pulsing when I arrived just now.

15
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:55,239
I’ve asked Hao Chen
to seal the entrance.

16
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:56,919
This is not the best time to speak.

17
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:58,988
We need to return to Xuyang Peak

18
00:03:58,989 --> 00:04:01,079
to set up a formation
in order to stabilize it.

19
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,820
- Follow me.
- Yes.

20
00:04:05,880 --> 00:04:07,220
Xuan Ji!

21
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:10,919
Are you out of your mind?

22
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:13,999
You would’ve been dead if your
Uncle Heng Yang and Senior Hao Chen

23
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,359
didn’t arrive in time!

24
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:17,719
Tell me! How did you
enter the secret ground?

25
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:18,980
I...

26
00:04:20,880 --> 00:04:22,518
- Father.
- Don’t call me that!

27
00:04:22,519 --> 00:04:25,099
I’m speaking as the sect leader now.

28
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:27,750
I...

29
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:32,879
Sect leader, I
really have no idea.

30
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:36,559
Maybe we entered by accident
because the barrier was too weak.

31
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:37,839
Is that true?

32
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:39,559
I’m not lying.

33
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:41,959
I will bear responsibility
for my mistakes.

34
00:04:41,960 --> 00:04:46,041
You can hit or punish me, but
please don’t blame Little Stammer.

35
00:04:46,042 --> 00:04:47,319
Hit you?

36
00:04:47,320 --> 00:04:48,660
That’ll never work.

37
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:54,199
I tried that since you were
young, but it didn’t work at all.

38
00:04:54,200 --> 00:04:57,373
You don’t feel any shame or pain.

39
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:00,759
The secret ground is
our sect’s forbidden ground.

40
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:03,260
You hid in there instead
of doing your training.

41
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:06,479
You even brought a stranger there!

42
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:08,782
You treat the laws of Shaoyang Sect
as if it was nothing!

43
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:11,995
Since young, you have lost all senses.

44
00:05:11,996 --> 00:05:14,559
And we allowed you to do as you please
because of that.

45
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:17,540
But I didn’t expect you to so spoiled!

46
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:20,639
From now on, I will never tolerate
what you do anymore.

47
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:24,199
The secret ground is of
utmost importance to our sect.

48
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:27,559
If you trespass the area,
you’ll pay the consequences.

49
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:30,839
From today onwards, you’ll reflect
your actions in Mingxia Cave!

50
00:05:30,840 --> 00:05:34,359
You’ll only be able to return
when you realize your mistakes!

51
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:35,679
Mingxia Cave?

52
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:37,119
Father, only disciples who had committed

53
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:39,127
serious crimes will be
sent to Mingxia Cave!

54
00:05:39,128 --> 00:05:41,516
It’s damp and dark over there.

55
00:05:41,517 --> 00:05:42,879
My sister mustn’t go there!

56
00:05:42,880 --> 00:05:46,079
Master, please
rescind your order.

57
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:47,439
My junior is young and ignorant.

58
00:05:47,440 --> 00:05:48,959
This punishment is too heavy for her.

59
00:05:48,960 --> 00:05:50,839
Master, please have mercy on her.

60
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:52,919
In our sect, we have our own rules.

61
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:56,380
I can’t just let her off
because she’s my daughter!

62
00:05:57,160 --> 00:05:59,275
- Father!
- Keep quiet!

63
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:04,943
- Sect Leader Chu, about this...
- Hero Yu.

64
00:06:04,944 --> 00:06:10,319
Regarding your intrusion, I’ll
report it to the elders in your sect.

65
00:06:10,320 --> 00:06:12,853
I’m handling the matters of my sect now.

66
00:06:12,854 --> 00:06:14,434
Please don’t interrupt.

67
00:06:18,449 --> 00:06:20,023
Aunt Ying Hong!

68
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:24,319
Ling Long, according to the rules
of Shaoyang Sect,

69
00:06:24,320 --> 00:06:27,254
those who enter the forbidden ground
will be sent to Mingxia Cave.

70
00:06:27,255 --> 00:06:28,504
There are no exceptions.

71
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:40,300
Master, the vice palace lord
of Lize Palace is here.

72
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:42,420
- Invite him here.
- Yes.

73
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:49,681
Sect Leader Chu, you called
me here in such a hurry.

74
00:06:49,682 --> 00:06:51,342
What exactly is going on?

75
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:54,668
Why are they kneeling...

76
00:06:59,436 --> 00:07:00,749
Where’s your mask?

77
00:07:05,880 --> 00:07:08,620
My lord, I’ve lost it.

78
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:11,060
You lost it?

79
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:13,980
How dare you say that!

80
00:07:14,640 --> 00:07:15,892
Vice palace lord,

81
00:07:16,436 --> 00:07:19,719
although the Flower Session
will be held in our sect,

82
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:20,999
that doesn’t mean that

83
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:23,879
all the areas in our sect
are open to the public.

84
00:07:23,880 --> 00:07:26,132
Please keep an eye on your disciple.

85
00:07:26,133 --> 00:07:29,925
Places other than Xuyang Peak
are closed to the public.

86
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:36,220
Sect Leader Chu,
this is our fault.

87
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:38,406
Yu Si Feng!

88
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:47,239
Sect Leader Chu, it was my fault
that I entered the forbidden ground.

89
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:50,959
But I left my mask in there.

90
00:07:50,960 --> 00:07:55,452
- Please allow me to enter...
- Impossible.

91
00:07:58,640 --> 00:08:02,519
So, he actually entered the
forbidden ground of Shaoyang Sect.

92
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:04,740
He’s digging his own grave.

93
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:10,679
Sect Leader Chu, what exactly
is in the forbidden ground?

94
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:12,479
My disciple was hurt in there.

95
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:16,879
And you tried to punish them severely
because of that.

96
00:08:16,880 --> 00:08:19,820
There are forbidden grounds
in Lize Palace as well.

97
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:23,559
Vice palace lord,

98
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:28,319
I’ve never tried to find out
what’s inside your forbidden ground.

99
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:30,119
Of course.

100
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:31,919
Every sect has their secrets.

101
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:34,839
We must never reveal them.

102
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:37,345
I’ll bring this rebellious disciple
of mine back.

103
00:08:37,346 --> 00:08:39,365
And punish him severely.

104
00:08:42,680 --> 00:08:45,216
Sect leader, ever since
our sect was formed,

105
00:08:45,217 --> 00:08:49,083
us in the Qingyang Peak
have used divination to

106
00:08:49,084 --> 00:08:51,279
assist Xuyang Peak in protecting
the secret ground.

107
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:54,879
Now, Senior Heng Yang has
set up a formation in Xuyang Peak

108
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:56,559
in order to stabilize the barrier.

109
00:08:56,560 --> 00:09:00,559
But I’m still concerned about something.

110
00:09:00,560 --> 00:09:04,820
Protecting the secret ground is
Shaoyang Sect’s main mission.

111
00:09:05,400 --> 00:09:07,180
Please tell me what’s on your mind.

112
00:09:08,920 --> 00:09:12,940
I’m still concerned about
Xuan Ji’s intrusion.

113
00:09:15,040 --> 00:09:16,919
Sixteen years ago,

114
00:09:16,920 --> 00:09:20,239
when the heavenly officers
came down to seal the secret ground,

115
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:24,079
they said that the barrier would
become weak in 25 years.

116
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:30,679
Maybe, Xuan Ji found the weak spot
by accident and managed to enter.

117
00:09:30,680 --> 00:09:32,060
Besides that,

118
00:09:34,040 --> 00:09:36,679
I can’t think of any other reasons.

119
00:09:36,680 --> 00:09:39,239
I hope that would be the case.

120
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:42,239
Senior, do you still remember
what our master said before?

121
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:45,799
He said an emotionless person
will activate the Jade Cup.

122
00:09:45,800 --> 00:09:49,159
For the past 16 years, Xuan
Ji hasn’t shed tears at all.

123
00:09:49,160 --> 00:09:51,679
She never showed any emotions.

124
00:09:51,680 --> 00:09:54,799
And now, she had managed
to enter the secret ground.

125
00:09:54,800 --> 00:09:57,719
Will she be the one
to activate the Jade Cup?

126
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:59,039
No!

127
00:09:59,040 --> 00:10:00,559
That’s impossible.

128
00:10:00,560 --> 00:10:02,559
I hope I’m wrong,

129
00:10:02,560 --> 00:10:05,639
but we must be very careful
when the secret ground is at stake!

130
00:10:05,640 --> 00:10:08,860
If Xuan Ji is the chosen person,

131
00:10:09,400 --> 00:10:11,820
the entire Shaoyang Sect
will be in danger!

132
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:16,839
You mean...

133
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:18,959
Why don’t we lock her up in Mingxia Cave

134
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:22,399
before we find out the truth?

135
00:10:22,400 --> 00:10:23,746
No!

136
00:10:24,760 --> 00:10:26,500
Mingxia Cave?

137
00:11:11,440 --> 00:11:14,279
Xuan Ji!

138
00:11:14,280 --> 00:11:15,919
- Ling Long!
- Xuan Ji!

139
00:11:15,920 --> 00:11:17,999
- I have something to tell you!
- Me too!

140
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:19,516
Listen to me first!

141
00:11:19,517 --> 00:11:21,239
I overheard Father and
Uncle Lu Yang’s conversation just now.

142
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:23,319
You showed no emotion and
you entered the secret ground.

143
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:25,519
Now, they want to lock you up
in Mingxia Cave forever!

144
00:11:25,520 --> 00:11:27,159
- Is that scary?
- Of course!

145
00:11:27,160 --> 00:11:29,279
Only those who had committed
serious crimes

146
00:11:29,280 --> 00:11:31,439
or lost themselves
will be locked up there.

147
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:33,516
It’s smelly, dirty, dark
and damp in there.

148
00:11:33,517 --> 00:11:35,879
I heard that you can hear
the cries of people there too.

149
00:11:35,880 --> 00:11:37,700
They’ll cry every night! It’s very scary!

150
00:11:38,680 --> 00:11:41,199
It’s fine. I’m not afraid.

151
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:42,958
Do you know the meaning of forever?

152
00:11:42,959 --> 00:11:45,065
It means that you won’t be able
to come out!

153
00:11:45,066 --> 00:11:46,825
You’ll be stuck in there forever!

154
00:11:46,826 --> 00:11:48,166
Are you willing to do so?

155
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:52,256
- What should I do then?
- You should cry.

156
00:11:52,257 --> 00:11:55,909
When Father sees you cry, he’ll
know that you’re not emotionless.

157
00:11:55,910 --> 00:11:57,168
And he won’t lock you up in there.

158
00:11:57,169 --> 00:11:59,999
But I don’t know how to cry.

159
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:01,999
You’re on the verge of death, you know?

160
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:04,777
How about you think of
the days when I took away your puppet?

161
00:12:04,778 --> 00:12:06,352
Your favourite puppet.

162
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:10,159
It’s fine. Just take it.

163
00:12:10,160 --> 00:12:11,599
Just take it if you like it.

164
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:14,900
What if you never see me or Father again?

165
00:12:16,640 --> 00:12:18,766
Or think about Mother.

166
00:12:18,767 --> 00:12:22,599
Think about the days when
Mother fed us personally.

167
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:24,020
Every time I think of that,

168
00:12:24,021 --> 00:12:26,223
my chest would feel stuffy
and I would cry.

169
00:12:26,224 --> 00:12:27,889
Do you feel the same way?

170
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:35,490
What should I do?

171
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:40,079
I have an idea!

172
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:41,362
What idea?

173
00:13:01,160 --> 00:13:02,490
Let’s go!

174
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:13,735
Xuan Ji!

175
00:13:14,520 --> 00:13:15,686
Xuan Ji!

176
00:13:15,687 --> 00:13:17,599
- Ling Long.
- Don’t go!

177
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:20,279
Aunt Ying Hong, please
let me send her off.

178
00:13:20,280 --> 00:13:21,980
I can’t bear to part with her.

179
00:13:22,680 --> 00:13:25,079
You must take good care of yourself.

180
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:26,420
Let’s hug.

181
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:31,599
What is this?

182
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:33,041
Chilli powder.

183
00:13:33,042 --> 00:13:35,559
Keep this a secret. Let’s go.

184
00:13:35,560 --> 00:13:36,873
Father!

185
00:13:37,880 --> 00:13:40,719
Father, Xuan Ji knows her mistakes now.

186
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:44,639
She knows her mistakes
and she feels bad about them.

187
00:13:44,640 --> 00:13:47,340
Look, her eyes are swollen
from crying too much.

188
00:13:49,560 --> 00:13:50,888
Is that true?

189
00:13:52,960 --> 00:13:55,119
- Xuan Ji.
- It’s true.

190
00:13:55,120 --> 00:13:56,459
Stop crying now.

191
00:13:58,880 --> 00:14:01,660
Stop crying. Father will be sad
if you continue this.

192
00:14:05,520 --> 00:14:07,079
What’s wrong with your eyes?

193
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:08,360
Let me see.

194
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:17,260
Stop fooling around! Bring her away!

195
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:20,394
Please don’t!

196
00:14:20,395 --> 00:14:23,079
- Xuan Ji!
- Ling Long!

197
00:14:23,080 --> 00:14:24,366
Father!

198
00:14:35,160 --> 00:14:40,660
- Let me out!
- Let me out!

199
00:14:41,520 --> 00:14:47,300
- Let me out!
- Let me out!

200
00:14:50,360 --> 00:14:54,500
- Let me out!
- Let me out!

201
00:14:56,640 --> 00:15:01,620
- Let me out!
- Let me out!

202
00:15:02,240 --> 00:15:06,380
- Let me out!
- Let me out!

203
00:15:08,920 --> 00:15:14,399
Losing the mask will put the
entire Lize Palace in danger.

204
00:15:14,400 --> 00:15:15,999
You’re not the only one affected.

205
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:17,519
You should treat it as your own flesh.

206
00:15:17,520 --> 00:15:20,700
You mustn’t take it off
in public, let alone lose it.

207
00:15:26,080 --> 00:15:27,350
Ruo Yu,

208
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:30,502
don’t tell me you’re feeling sorry

209
00:15:30,503 --> 00:15:32,460
for someone who has broken the rules?

210
00:15:33,480 --> 00:15:34,897
Continue!

211
00:15:38,560 --> 00:15:42,399
Yu Si Feng, not only
did you lose your mask,

212
00:15:42,400 --> 00:15:44,359
you didn’t manage to retrieve it.

213
00:15:44,360 --> 00:15:46,020
What shall we do with you?

214
00:15:47,440 --> 00:15:49,519
I deserve the 13 Punishments.

215
00:15:49,520 --> 00:15:50,940
Whip him harder!

216
00:16:02,560 --> 00:16:04,759
Yu Si Feng, how do you explain this?

217
00:16:04,760 --> 00:16:09,740
I would never dare to break
the rules of Lize Palace.

218
00:16:10,320 --> 00:16:11,879
I’m willing to be punished

219
00:16:11,880 --> 00:16:16,540
in order to show my loyalty
to Lize Palace.

220
00:16:18,280 --> 00:16:20,679
Our lord thinks highly of you.

221
00:16:20,680 --> 00:16:23,319
He even wanted to bestow
the Gold Feather Medallion to you.

222
00:16:23,320 --> 00:16:24,719
Look at you right now.

223
00:16:24,720 --> 00:16:28,159
You had to receive the 13 Punishments
when you went out for once.

224
00:16:28,160 --> 00:16:32,180
You’ve disappointed our lord.

225
00:16:36,280 --> 00:16:37,601
What are you doing?

226
00:16:38,360 --> 00:16:40,439
Bring him back to Lize Palace
for further punishment.

227
00:16:40,440 --> 00:16:41,919
Vice palace lord,

228
00:16:41,920 --> 00:16:45,159
Yu Si Feng had registered his name
for the Flower Session.

229
00:16:45,160 --> 00:16:46,999
He had sent his name to them.

230
00:16:47,000 --> 00:16:49,599
And he has been chosen
for the Flower Picking Mission too.

231
00:16:49,600 --> 00:16:53,740
If he returns to Lize Palace
now, the Flower Session will be...

232
00:16:54,448 --> 00:16:57,079
I forgot about that.

233
00:16:57,080 --> 00:16:59,799
Flower Session is a huge event
among the Five Great Sects.

234
00:16:59,800 --> 00:17:01,559
If he doesn’t attend the event
after putting his name,

235
00:17:01,560 --> 00:17:04,239
the name of Lize Palace will be affected.

236
00:17:04,240 --> 00:17:07,679
Elder Luo, what should we do?

237
00:17:07,680 --> 00:17:09,838
Let him stay for now.

238
00:17:09,839 --> 00:17:13,020
Our lord will arrive at Xuyang Peak
before the session starts.

239
00:17:13,839 --> 00:17:16,799
I think we can report to our lord for now.

240
00:17:16,800 --> 00:17:19,799
He’ll receive his punishment
after the Flower Session.

241
00:17:19,800 --> 00:17:23,260
He won’t get to
escape his punishment.

242
00:17:26,920 --> 00:17:29,559
Seems like you’re safe for now.

243
00:17:29,560 --> 00:17:32,479
If I were you, I would try to

244
00:17:32,480 --> 00:17:36,159
retrieve the mask before our lord
arrives at Xuyang Peak.

245
00:17:36,160 --> 00:17:39,540
You would only have a chance
to turn things around by doing so.

246
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:49,359
Si Feng, this ointment
is odourless and tasteless.

247
00:17:49,360 --> 00:17:51,580
No one will discover this.

248
00:17:52,880 --> 00:17:55,220
I heard that many disciples

249
00:17:56,040 --> 00:17:59,559
ended their lives in order
to avoid further suffering.

250
00:17:59,560 --> 00:18:01,599
You’ll receive heavy punishments
when you return.

251
00:18:01,600 --> 00:18:03,020
Have you thought of a solution?

252
00:18:04,160 --> 00:18:05,759
Under the circumstances,

253
00:18:05,760 --> 00:18:08,919
you can only try and
contribute more to the sect

254
00:18:08,920 --> 00:18:11,439
so that the lord would
give you another chance.

255
00:18:11,440 --> 00:18:14,919
I heard that the monster
you’ll be hunting is Gudiao.

256
00:18:14,920 --> 00:18:16,359
It’s a vicious beast.

257
00:18:16,360 --> 00:18:17,919
But if you hunt it successfully,

258
00:18:17,920 --> 00:18:19,420
it’ll be a huge contribution to our sect.

259
00:18:59,840 --> 00:19:01,220
It finally stopped.

260
00:19:02,920 --> 00:19:04,248
I’m so sleepy.

261
00:19:26,640 --> 00:19:28,500
We entered from here last time.

262
00:19:31,080 --> 00:19:33,300
There are no weak spots
outside the secret ground.

263
00:19:34,560 --> 00:19:36,540
Don’t tell me I need to
find Chu Xuan Ji again?

264
00:19:52,960 --> 00:19:54,303
Dan Ping,

265
00:19:54,880 --> 00:19:56,719
you must be blaming me right now.

266
00:19:56,720 --> 00:19:58,540
You told me to take care of our daughter.

267
00:19:59,120 --> 00:20:03,519
But now, Xuan Ji had
committed a serious crime.

268
00:20:03,520 --> 00:20:05,039
What should I do?

269
00:20:05,040 --> 00:20:07,060
What should I do now?

270
00:20:07,600 --> 00:20:11,508
Father, you should send
me to Mingxia Cave as well.

271
00:20:11,509 --> 00:20:13,799
I feel sorry for my little sister.

272
00:20:13,800 --> 00:20:16,660
Master, please let Xuan Ji off.

273
00:20:17,320 --> 00:20:19,980
- Master, please let Xuan Ji off.
- Master, please let Xuan Ji off.

274
00:20:21,680 --> 00:20:23,159
Senior!

275
00:20:23,160 --> 00:20:25,664
Senior, the protection rock
is vibrating again.

276
00:20:28,040 --> 00:20:30,060
- Let’s have a look.
- Father!

277
00:20:32,560 --> 00:20:35,180
Don’t ever mention that matter
in front of me.

278
00:20:50,720 --> 00:20:51,999
Who’s there?

279
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:54,140
How dare you intrude
the secret ground of Shaoyang Sect?

280
00:20:57,280 --> 00:21:01,879
Greetings, Uncle, Aunt Ying
Hong and Uncle He Yang.

281
00:21:01,880 --> 00:21:03,368
It’s been quite a rush.

282
00:21:03,369 --> 00:21:04,919
And I didn’t greet my elders.

283
00:21:04,920 --> 00:21:06,371
Please forgive me.

284
00:21:06,920 --> 00:21:08,319
That’s fine.

285
00:21:08,320 --> 00:21:11,679
You and your master were trying to
stabilize the protective barrier.

286
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:13,460
You don’t need to be too courteous.

287
00:21:14,000 --> 00:21:16,534
You were unskilled when Senior Heng Yang

288
00:21:16,535 --> 00:21:17,999
accepted you as his disciple
ten years ago.

289
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:19,795
I didn’t expect you to be this powerful

290
00:21:19,796 --> 00:21:22,113
just after ten years of training.

291
00:21:22,114 --> 00:21:24,799
I witnessed how you resealed the barrier.

292
00:21:24,800 --> 00:21:28,719
Seems like you’ve exceeded
the ten levels of Yang Jue Skill.

293
00:21:28,720 --> 00:21:31,780
And it seems like you’ve mastered

294
00:21:31,781 --> 00:21:34,039
the Heartless Tactics of
Xuyang Peak as well.

295
00:21:34,040 --> 00:21:35,319
I was untalented.

296
00:21:35,320 --> 00:21:37,359
I only mastered the Heartless Tactics
not long ago.

297
00:21:37,360 --> 00:21:38,999
Only then, Master sent me here.

298
00:21:39,000 --> 00:21:40,879
You’re too humble.

299
00:21:40,880 --> 00:21:43,879
You’re this exceptional
when you’re so young.

300
00:21:43,880 --> 00:21:46,500
It’s no wonder you’re the favourite
disciple of Senior Heng Yang.

301
00:21:47,240 --> 00:21:50,310
I suppose Senior Heng
Yang is still in Xuyang Peak?

302
00:21:50,311 --> 00:21:52,799
The base of the protective barrier
is located at Xuyang Peak.

303
00:21:52,800 --> 00:21:56,199
Master needs to stay there for some days
in order to stabilize the barrier.

304
00:21:56,200 --> 00:21:58,497
Now that the Rahu Star
and Ketu Star are attracting each other,

305
00:21:58,498 --> 00:22:00,399
the protective barrier is getting
more unstable.

306
00:22:00,400 --> 00:22:03,159
That’s why Master sent me
to Shouyang Peak to check it out.

307
00:22:03,160 --> 00:22:04,414
And to strengthen the barrier.

308
00:22:04,415 --> 00:22:05,839
So that Shaoyang Sect will be safe.

309
00:22:05,840 --> 00:22:08,340
That’s the reason behind
Shaoyang Sect’s formation.

310
00:22:09,680 --> 00:22:13,799
Uncle, where’s the junior who
had entered the secret ground?

311
00:22:13,800 --> 00:22:16,300
I’ve sent her to Mingxia Cave.

312
00:22:16,880 --> 00:22:20,479
She’s lazy, and ordinary.

313
00:22:20,480 --> 00:22:22,740
It’s impossible for her
to unseal the barrier.

314
00:22:23,320 --> 00:22:26,519
I think there are
abnormalities within the barrier.

315
00:22:26,520 --> 00:22:28,504
That’s why she got in by accident.

316
00:22:28,505 --> 00:22:31,820
Hao Chen, please investigate
this matter for me.

317
00:22:32,920 --> 00:22:34,225
Yes.

318
00:23:03,040 --> 00:23:04,839
Seems like I can’t get up there.

319
00:23:04,840 --> 00:23:06,700
I can’t ask Chu Xuan Ji
about the secret ground now.

320
00:23:07,400 --> 00:23:09,540
Why are you here
in the middle of the night?

321
00:23:11,960 --> 00:23:13,439
Without Aunt Ying Hong’s pass,

322
00:23:13,440 --> 00:23:15,199
it’s impossible for us
to ascend Xiaoyang Peak.

323
00:23:15,200 --> 00:23:16,799
You won’t be able to enter Mingxia Cave.

324
00:23:16,800 --> 00:23:18,799
Can’t I just have a look?

325
00:23:18,800 --> 00:23:21,719
Mingxia Cave is dark and creepy.

326
00:23:21,720 --> 00:23:23,639
And Xuan Ji didn’t train before.

327
00:23:23,640 --> 00:23:26,159
I wonder if she could withstand it?

328
00:23:26,160 --> 00:23:27,799
If Xuan Ji doesn’t learn how to cry,

329
00:23:27,800 --> 00:23:30,759
she’ll never be able to prove that
she’s not emotionless.

330
00:23:30,760 --> 00:23:32,319
And she’ll never come out.

331
00:23:32,320 --> 00:23:34,079
We should think of other ways.

332
00:23:34,080 --> 00:23:35,873
- But...
- Let’s go.

333
00:23:40,280 --> 00:23:43,340
Will Chu Xuan Ji be able to leave
if she cries?

334
00:24:08,200 --> 00:24:09,820
Let me out!

335
00:24:12,280 --> 00:24:14,199
Let me out!

336
00:24:14,200 --> 00:24:16,460
Let me out!

337
00:24:21,680 --> 00:24:23,660
Let me out!

338
00:24:26,040 --> 00:24:28,119
Let me out!

339
00:24:28,120 --> 00:24:29,479
So noisy.

340
00:24:29,480 --> 00:24:30,799
Little Stammer.

341
00:24:30,800 --> 00:24:32,759
I took away his mask.

342
00:24:32,760 --> 00:24:34,980
Does he have to receive
the same punishment?

343
00:24:36,600 --> 00:24:38,180
Let me out!

344
00:24:40,480 --> 00:24:41,820
Let me out!

345
00:24:49,760 --> 00:24:52,719
The two stars are getting closer.

346
00:24:52,720 --> 00:24:54,039
Did you guys notice that?

347
00:24:54,040 --> 00:24:55,479
Yes.

348
00:24:55,480 --> 00:24:56,919
Maybe it’s a sign that

349
00:24:56,920 --> 00:24:59,079
the primordial spirits of Mosha Star,
Rahu Star and Ketu Star,

350
00:24:59,080 --> 00:25:00,620
are getting closer to their souls.

351
00:25:01,240 --> 00:25:03,559
But my lord, don’t you worry.

352
00:25:03,560 --> 00:25:06,709
I’ve sent spies to join
the Flower Session.

353
00:25:06,710 --> 00:25:08,890
They won’t disappoint you.

354
00:25:09,480 --> 00:25:13,119
In addition, according to
our branch in Mount Lutai,

355
00:25:13,120 --> 00:25:15,959
they’ve used Tengu to capture

356
00:25:15,960 --> 00:25:18,999
the merman who knows
how to obtain the Divine Weapon.

357
00:25:19,000 --> 00:25:20,799
Wolf is interrogating him now.

358
00:25:20,800 --> 00:25:24,892
Good. Tell Wolf to use
any methods available

359
00:25:24,893 --> 00:25:26,900
in order to extract information.

360
00:25:28,040 --> 00:25:29,365
Yes, my lord.

361
00:25:35,249 --> 00:25:36,549
Xuan Ji!

362
00:25:37,640 --> 00:25:39,399
Xuan Ji!

363
00:25:39,400 --> 00:25:40,999
Xuan Ji, how are you feeling?

364
00:25:41,000 --> 00:25:42,411
Why are you frozen?

365
00:25:48,320 --> 00:25:51,512
Sixth Senior, I’m
not cold at all.

366
00:25:51,513 --> 00:25:54,239
My body is shaking on its own.

367
00:25:54,240 --> 00:25:59,679
Sixth Senior, I don’t want
to stay in this cave alone.

368
00:25:59,680 --> 00:26:03,319
Will Father lock me here forever?

369
00:26:03,320 --> 00:26:07,481
I... I’ve always been
an embarrassment.

370
00:26:07,482 --> 00:26:09,359
And I created trouble
for Shaoyang Sect as well.

371
00:26:09,360 --> 00:26:12,180
Will he really abandon me?

372
00:26:14,280 --> 00:26:16,159
Xuan Ji, don’t say that.

373
00:26:16,160 --> 00:26:18,645
Master is the sect leader.
He has his own difficulties.

374
00:26:18,646 --> 00:26:20,039
But he does care about you.

375
00:26:20,040 --> 00:26:23,439
I came here today because
Master wanted me to send you some food.

376
00:26:23,440 --> 00:26:24,872
He misses you.

377
00:26:24,873 --> 00:26:27,318
And Ling Long and I are worried about you.

378
00:26:27,319 --> 00:26:28,983
We’re trying to find a solution.

379
00:26:28,984 --> 00:26:31,269
You mustn’t give up now.

380
00:26:31,270 --> 00:26:32,650
Will there be a solution?

381
00:26:33,187 --> 00:26:35,959
About that, we can
think about it later.

382
00:26:35,960 --> 00:26:38,839
Now, you should eat.

383
00:26:38,840 --> 00:26:40,039
You must eat.

384
00:26:40,040 --> 00:26:42,479
You won’t be able to survive
if you got sick.

385
00:26:42,480 --> 00:26:44,919
Ling Long made this porridge herself.

386
00:26:44,920 --> 00:26:47,103
She said she needed to
do something for you

387
00:26:47,104 --> 00:26:49,479
since Master wasn’t willing to
let her come.

388
00:26:49,480 --> 00:26:50,691
Come.

389
00:26:50,692 --> 00:26:52,385
Ling Long made this herself.

390
00:26:52,386 --> 00:26:54,446
I must finish this.

391
00:27:00,920 --> 00:27:02,359
What’s wrong?

392
00:27:02,360 --> 00:27:03,733
Is it too hot?

393
00:27:08,480 --> 00:27:13,359
Sixth Senior, I can
taste the porridge now!

394
00:27:13,360 --> 00:27:14,661
What did you say?

395
00:27:18,240 --> 00:27:21,759
But why is this porridge so unpalatable?

396
00:27:21,760 --> 00:27:24,540
How did you finish the food
she made for you?

397
00:27:25,520 --> 00:27:28,260
She’ll be sad if I don’t finish them.

398
00:27:29,320 --> 00:27:30,700
You can taste food now?

399
00:27:32,240 --> 00:27:34,959
Sixth Senior, there are
so many dishes here.

400
00:27:34,960 --> 00:27:36,399
- Do they have different tastes?
- Yeah.

401
00:27:36,400 --> 00:27:38,319
Here, try this.

402
00:27:38,320 --> 00:27:40,660
- This is salty.
- Salty?

403
00:27:45,720 --> 00:27:47,008
It’s delicious!

404
00:27:47,009 --> 00:27:50,458
Try this. This is sweet
with a hint of sourness.

405
00:27:55,720 --> 00:27:57,239
This is delicious!

406
00:27:57,240 --> 00:27:58,559
This is spicy.

407
00:27:58,560 --> 00:28:00,141
- Come, try this.
- Spicy?

408
00:28:05,000 --> 00:28:06,599
This is the best!

409
00:28:06,600 --> 00:28:08,368
Slowly, don’t choke yourself.

410
00:28:10,800 --> 00:28:14,079
Xuan Ji, what
exactly is going on?

411
00:28:14,080 --> 00:28:15,519
You...

412
00:28:15,520 --> 00:28:17,620
Have you recovered
the other five senses as well?

413
00:28:18,160 --> 00:28:19,559
Do you know how to cry now?

414
00:28:19,560 --> 00:28:22,340
If you do, Master will let you out.

415
00:28:23,760 --> 00:28:25,340
- Cry?
- Try it.

416
00:28:37,120 --> 00:28:38,620
Are there tears?

417
00:28:42,920 --> 00:28:44,479
Xuan Ji recovered her taste?

418
00:28:44,480 --> 00:28:46,719
Did she recover the other senses as well?

419
00:28:46,720 --> 00:28:48,919
Can she cry now?

420
00:28:48,920 --> 00:28:51,719
- That’s the most important thing.
- Only her taste.

421
00:28:51,720 --> 00:28:54,679
She doesn’t even know
how she recovered her taste.

422
00:28:54,680 --> 00:28:57,879
Maybe it’s connected to the secret ground.

423
00:28:57,880 --> 00:29:00,039
Maybe? It’s because
you didn’t ask enough questions.

424
00:29:00,040 --> 00:29:01,350
Maybe? My foot.

425
00:29:02,280 --> 00:29:05,959
Lady, if you don’t believe me,
you can go to Xiaoyang Peak.

426
00:29:05,960 --> 00:29:08,759
I wouldn’t need to listen to you
if I could go there.

427
00:29:08,760 --> 00:29:10,110
I’m so furious.

428
00:29:17,760 --> 00:29:19,759
Whose Demon Manual is this?

429
00:29:19,760 --> 00:29:22,420
- Demon Manual?
- There’s a bookmark as well.

430
00:29:26,480 --> 00:29:29,639
Gudiao is vicious,
its horns are terrifying.

431
00:29:29,640 --> 00:29:31,199
Its horns can be refined into a rare item.

432
00:29:31,200 --> 00:29:33,879
The item can reduce anyone into tears.
Its name is Weeping Tears.

433
00:29:33,880 --> 00:29:35,239
Who put this here?

434
00:29:35,240 --> 00:29:37,599
I’m sure it’s the people
who wanted to save Xuan Ji.

435
00:29:37,600 --> 00:29:38,959
Weeping Tears?

436
00:29:38,960 --> 00:29:41,220
Xuan Ji will be saved
if she acquires that.

437
00:29:41,795 --> 00:29:42,999
Yeah.

438
00:29:43,000 --> 00:29:46,980
But where do we find this Gudiao?

439
00:29:48,800 --> 00:29:50,199
It’s written here.

440
00:29:50,200 --> 00:29:53,199
The demon they’ll hunt
for the Flower Session is Gudiao.

441
00:29:53,200 --> 00:29:55,079
This is great! Father is in Shouyang Hall.

442
00:29:55,080 --> 00:29:56,559
He’s briefing the Five Great Sects
about the mission.

443
00:29:56,560 --> 00:29:58,319
- Let’s go there now.
- Go there?

444
00:29:58,320 --> 00:30:00,279
Many guards will be patrolling there.
I’m sure the hall will be full.

445
00:30:00,280 --> 00:30:01,919
Will we be able to enter the hall?

446
00:30:01,920 --> 00:30:05,879
Didn’t you say you’re getting better
in your Burrowing Spell?

447
00:30:05,880 --> 00:30:07,479
We’ll use that spell then.

448
00:30:07,480 --> 00:30:10,679
You seemed comfortable
in ordering me around, huh?

449
00:30:10,680 --> 00:30:11,877
Let’s go.

450
00:30:11,878 --> 00:30:16,279
Everyone, as you all
know, the Flower Session

451
00:30:16,280 --> 00:30:19,313
is organized so that the Five Great Sects
can spar with each other.

452
00:30:19,314 --> 00:30:21,174
And showcase the talents
hidden within each sect.

453
00:30:21,880 --> 00:30:24,011
Those who are under 16

454
00:30:24,012 --> 00:30:27,066
and had never attended
previous sessions before

455
00:30:27,067 --> 00:30:29,319
may showcase their talents here.

456
00:30:29,320 --> 00:30:34,774
As righteous sects, we still
need to abide by our sworn duties.

457
00:30:34,775 --> 00:30:36,839
That is, to slay demons.

458
00:30:36,840 --> 00:30:38,848
So that the world can be at peace.

459
00:30:38,849 --> 00:30:41,829
We must never forget that.

460
00:30:42,440 --> 00:30:44,239
The people of each sects
shall spar together.

461
00:30:44,240 --> 00:30:48,599
The final winner will fight
with the demon and try to slay it

462
00:30:48,600 --> 00:30:52,525
in order to retrieve the flower
that we’ve put on top of it.

463
00:30:52,526 --> 00:30:57,439
Our mission is to capture
the demon and bring it back.

464
00:30:57,440 --> 00:30:59,639
This mission is different
from a normal contest.

465
00:30:59,640 --> 00:31:01,079
It is very dangerous.

466
00:31:01,080 --> 00:31:05,376
That’s why we decided to draw
lots, just like what we did last time.

467
00:31:05,880 --> 00:31:09,159
The lots have been placed.

468
00:31:09,160 --> 00:31:13,199
This year, Lord Dong
Fang will draw the lots.

469
00:31:13,200 --> 00:31:14,860
Brother Dong Fang, please.

470
00:31:15,920 --> 00:31:17,371
Our demon today

471
00:31:17,372 --> 00:31:19,620
is the demon who has been
wreaking havoc on Mount Lutai.

472
00:31:20,320 --> 00:31:23,020
Many villagers have been harmed.

473
00:31:23,600 --> 00:31:24,915
Those who had witnessed it

474
00:31:24,916 --> 00:31:27,159
said that its wings are
as wide as five feet.

475
00:31:27,160 --> 00:31:29,346
Its howl sounds like a child’s cry.

476
00:31:29,347 --> 00:31:31,183
And it devours human underwater.

477
00:31:31,184 --> 00:31:32,423
From these characteristics,

478
00:31:32,424 --> 00:31:37,359
I’m sure it is the long-lost
vicious beast, Gudiao.

479
00:31:37,360 --> 00:31:38,999
It’s Gudiao!

480
00:31:39,000 --> 00:31:40,968
Seems like the heavens are helping us.

481
00:31:40,969 --> 00:31:43,959
As long as we get Gudiao’s horns
and refined them into Weeping Tears,

482
00:31:43,960 --> 00:31:47,399
Xuan Ji can leave Mingxia Cave.

483
00:31:47,400 --> 00:31:49,299
Who’s been eavesdropping
on our conversation?

484
00:31:49,300 --> 00:31:50,572
Come out!

485
00:32:00,080 --> 00:32:01,500
Come out right now!

486
00:32:11,240 --> 00:32:12,485
Master.

487
00:32:14,240 --> 00:32:15,999
Why are you guys here?

488
00:32:16,000 --> 00:32:17,302
Aunt.

489
00:32:18,720 --> 00:32:20,370
They’re just kids.

490
00:32:20,371 --> 00:32:22,151
Elder Ling Shi,
you don’t need to be angry.

491
00:32:22,720 --> 00:32:24,559
They’re still young and ignorant.

492
00:32:24,560 --> 00:32:26,447
Sorry for the embarrassment.

493
00:32:26,448 --> 00:32:28,785
Two of you, get out immediately.

494
00:32:28,786 --> 00:32:30,679
So, it’s a misunderstanding.

495
00:32:30,680 --> 00:32:35,210
But everyone here
must participate in this event.

496
00:32:35,211 --> 00:32:38,119
If not, the rules will be broken.

497
00:32:38,120 --> 00:32:39,380
You!

498
00:32:40,080 --> 00:32:42,239
Father, I would like to join.

499
00:32:42,240 --> 00:32:43,544
I’ll capture Gudiao.

500
00:32:43,545 --> 00:32:45,279
I’ve trained for more than ten years.

501
00:32:45,280 --> 00:32:47,228
Please let me go.

502
00:32:47,229 --> 00:32:50,559
Good. Like father, like daughter.

503
00:32:50,560 --> 00:32:53,279
Miss Chu, I’m impressed.

504
00:32:53,280 --> 00:32:55,279
- You...
- The Shaoyang Sect

505
00:32:55,280 --> 00:32:56,919
has always treated demon slaying
as our mission.

506
00:32:56,920 --> 00:32:58,519
We will never retreat.

507
00:32:58,520 --> 00:33:00,759
Master, I would like to join as well.

508
00:33:00,760 --> 00:33:04,359
Seems like there are many
young talents in the Shaoyang Sect.

509
00:33:04,360 --> 00:33:06,498
Sect Leader Chu, you have nothing to fear.

510
00:33:07,440 --> 00:33:08,999
Fine.

511
00:33:09,000 --> 00:33:10,380
Since that’s the case,

512
00:33:10,960 --> 00:33:13,100
we should include their names.

513
00:33:14,160 --> 00:33:15,442
Master,

514
00:33:16,920 --> 00:33:18,237
I’ll write the names.

515
00:33:56,520 --> 00:33:59,180
We’ll start now.

516
00:34:03,920 --> 00:34:07,180
Let’s see who’ll be the first chosen one.

517
00:34:09,080 --> 00:34:12,700
The lord of Fuyu Island,
Dong Fang Qing Qi?

518
00:34:13,988 --> 00:34:15,678
Seems like I was lucky.

519
00:34:15,679 --> 00:34:17,208
I’m flattered.

520
00:34:17,760 --> 00:34:19,620
Let’s look at the second lot.

521
00:34:21,400 --> 00:34:25,994
Shaoyang Sect, the elder of
Xiaoyang Peak, Chu Ying Hong.

522
00:34:30,560 --> 00:34:32,860
I’m flattered.

523
00:34:34,360 --> 00:34:35,653
The third lot.

524
00:34:38,800 --> 00:34:43,671
The golden disciple of
Lize Palace, Yu Si Feng.

525
00:34:47,560 --> 00:34:48,999
It’s Yu Si Feng!

526
00:34:49,000 --> 00:34:50,419
He’s as handsome as always.

527
00:34:51,239 --> 00:34:52,542
You are something indeed.

528
00:34:53,400 --> 00:34:56,678
Seems like he has the same age as Xuan Ji.

529
00:34:56,679 --> 00:34:58,718
He’s barely old enough
to attend the session,

530
00:34:58,719 --> 00:35:01,039
yet he’s already chosen for the mission?

531
00:35:01,040 --> 00:35:03,060
Seems like he’s pretty powerful.

532
00:35:04,360 --> 00:35:05,780
The fourth lot.

533
00:35:06,560 --> 00:35:10,622
Shaoyang Sect, disciple of
Shouyang Peak, Zhong Min Yan.

534
00:35:16,400 --> 00:35:18,319
Seems like I was chosen.

535
00:35:18,320 --> 00:35:20,439
Elders, please forgive me.

536
00:35:20,440 --> 00:35:22,500
Let’s look at the fifth and sixth lot.

537
00:35:24,560 --> 00:35:27,439
Sect leader of
Shaoyang Sect, Chu Lei.

538
00:35:27,440 --> 00:35:30,980
Shaoyang Sect, disciple
of Xuyang Peak, Hao Chen.

539
00:35:33,560 --> 00:35:34,879
My father was chosen!

540
00:35:38,000 --> 00:35:39,959
It’s good that both our sect leader
and Hao Chen were chosen.

541
00:35:39,960 --> 00:35:42,740
I was afraid I couldn’t
take care of Min Hao on my own.

542
00:35:43,400 --> 00:35:47,500
Seems like the Shaoyang Sect
makes up the majority of the members.

543
00:35:48,320 --> 00:35:49,820
Let’s look at the last lot.

544
00:35:51,680 --> 00:35:53,220
It’s Shaoyang Sect again.

545
00:35:54,280 --> 00:35:57,580
Shaoyang Sect,
disciple of Xuyang Peak, Chu...

546
00:36:09,760 --> 00:36:11,260
Chu Xuan Ji.

547
00:36:26,280 --> 00:36:29,199
Master, I don’t know what happened either.

548
00:36:29,200 --> 00:36:32,759
My mind went blank,
my hand was shaking,

549
00:36:32,760 --> 00:36:34,959
and I wrote Xuan Ji instead of Ling Long.

550
00:36:34,960 --> 00:36:37,460
Master, please punish me.

551
00:36:38,080 --> 00:36:40,359
But Father, since that had happened,

552
00:36:40,360 --> 00:36:44,118
we must keep our words
since the other sects are observing us.

553
00:36:45,880 --> 00:36:48,559
Don’t think that I don’t know
what you two are plotting.

554
00:36:48,560 --> 00:36:52,169
So what if you can save her
from Mingxia Cave for now?

555
00:36:52,170 --> 00:36:54,599
Do you think you can really change her?

556
00:36:54,600 --> 00:36:59,199
But if we expose her to the world,
maybe she’ll recover her senses.

557
00:36:59,200 --> 00:37:02,444
Maybe she’ll feel happy,
sad, or something like that.

558
00:37:02,445 --> 00:37:03,719
Am I right?

559
00:37:03,720 --> 00:37:07,903
Senior, the protective
barrier is stable for now.

560
00:37:07,904 --> 00:37:11,239
And Junior Xuan Ji’s name was
included in the mission as well.

561
00:37:11,240 --> 00:37:14,519
We must keep our words. I think
we should let her out for now.

562
00:37:14,520 --> 00:37:17,119
And if she’s still emotionless
after the mission,

563
00:37:17,120 --> 00:37:18,876
we’ll send her back to Mingxia Cave.

564
00:37:18,877 --> 00:37:20,079
Yeah.

565
00:37:20,080 --> 00:37:21,740
Master, Senior is right.

566
00:37:25,320 --> 00:37:26,599
Fine.

567
00:37:26,600 --> 00:37:29,820
Since Hao Chen had said so,

568
00:37:30,840 --> 00:37:32,340
we’ll do just that.

569
00:37:51,400 --> 00:37:52,705
I’m so hungry.

570
00:37:54,440 --> 00:37:56,980
Why isn’t Sixth Senior here yet?

571
00:37:58,120 --> 00:37:59,461
Xuan Ji!

572
00:38:00,960 --> 00:38:02,233
Xuan Ji!

573
00:38:03,000 --> 00:38:04,340
Xuan Ji!

574
00:38:06,000 --> 00:38:07,306
Ling Long!

575
00:38:08,600 --> 00:38:10,359
Xuan Ji!

576
00:38:10,360 --> 00:38:12,060
- Ling Long!
- Xuan Ji!

577
00:38:12,920 --> 00:38:14,119
This place is so cold!

578
00:38:14,120 --> 00:38:16,239
- Ling Long!
- It must’ve been tough.

579
00:38:16,240 --> 00:38:17,540
Let me have a look.

580
00:38:18,160 --> 00:38:20,399
I’m fine. I’m not cold at all.

581
00:38:20,400 --> 00:38:22,359
Why are you hurt?

582
00:38:22,360 --> 00:38:24,119
Come, we’ll leave this place.

583
00:38:24,120 --> 00:38:26,940
Wait, Ling Long. Can I leave now?

584
00:38:28,800 --> 00:38:30,999
- Are you cold?
- Xuan Ji,

585
00:38:31,000 --> 00:38:32,620
you were chosen for the
Flower Picking Mission.

586
00:38:33,480 --> 00:38:34,759
Flower Picking Mission?

587
00:38:34,760 --> 00:38:36,639
But I have never met a demon before.

588
00:38:36,640 --> 00:38:38,159
How could I defeat it?

589
00:38:38,160 --> 00:38:40,239
Silly girl, you don’t need to do so.

590
00:38:40,240 --> 00:38:42,079
This is just a plan to save you.

591
00:38:42,080 --> 00:38:43,599
Let’s go, okay?

592
00:38:43,600 --> 00:38:44,999
What should we do in the future?

593
00:38:45,000 --> 00:38:46,679
I don’t want to return to this place.

594
00:38:46,680 --> 00:38:48,279
You won’t.

595
00:38:48,280 --> 00:38:49,599
We’ll proceed step by step.

596
00:38:49,600 --> 00:38:51,540
Let’s leave this place for now, okay?

597
00:38:52,680 --> 00:38:56,700
Sister, will I be able to enjoy
delicious food when I go out?

598
00:38:58,000 --> 00:39:01,039
You can eat as much as you want. Let’s go.

599
00:39:01,040 --> 00:39:02,660
- Let’s go!
- Let’s go.

600
00:39:05,880 --> 00:39:12,999
Si Feng, it is a must for disciples
of the Lize Palace to wear masks.

601
00:39:13,000 --> 00:39:15,999
First, outsiders will think twice
before approaching us.

602
00:39:16,000 --> 00:39:20,399
Second, it is used to
protect your true nature.

603
00:39:20,400 --> 00:39:23,140
So that you can be focused at all times.

604
00:39:26,120 --> 00:39:28,300
Since you’ve lost your mask,

605
00:39:29,040 --> 00:39:32,079
you mustn’t be distracted by other things.

606
00:39:32,080 --> 00:39:33,940
So that you’ll not commit another mistake.

607
00:39:34,840 --> 00:39:36,163
I understand.

608
00:39:54,840 --> 00:39:56,189
Chu Xuan Ji.

609
00:39:57,640 --> 00:39:58,973
Chu Xuan Ji.

610
00:40:00,600 --> 00:40:01,915
You’re here indeed.

611
00:40:02,920 --> 00:40:05,100
Little Stammer, it’s you?

612
00:40:06,120 --> 00:40:08,119
Why aren’t you a stammer anymore?

613
00:40:08,120 --> 00:40:09,430
I’m very smart.

614
00:40:10,080 --> 00:40:12,639
By the way, I’ve been worried
about you these few days.

615
00:40:12,640 --> 00:40:15,361
They said masks in Lize Palace
weren’t supposed to be removed.

616
00:40:15,362 --> 00:40:18,159
But I removed your mask. Are you okay?

617
00:40:18,160 --> 00:40:19,450
You don’t need to care.

618
00:40:21,440 --> 00:40:23,409
But Lize Palace is strange indeed.

619
00:40:23,410 --> 00:40:26,740
Why does everyone like
to hide their faces behind a mask?

620
00:40:28,440 --> 00:40:31,795
Little Stammer,
you have a little mole here.

621
00:40:31,796 --> 00:40:34,096
Do you cry a lot?

622
00:40:35,320 --> 00:40:37,199
I’ve never shed tears before.

623
00:40:37,200 --> 00:40:38,792
Chu Xuan Ji, listen up.

624
00:40:38,793 --> 00:40:40,197
I’m going to retrieve my mask.

625
00:40:40,198 --> 00:40:41,759
Bring me to the secret ground again.

626
00:40:41,760 --> 00:40:44,675
The secret ground? No way.

627
00:40:44,676 --> 00:40:47,422
I can agree with anything except for that.

628
00:40:47,423 --> 00:40:50,179
My father sent me to Mingxia Cave
for that. I had to suffer, you know?

629
00:40:50,180 --> 00:40:51,399
I’m not going.

630
00:40:51,400 --> 00:40:53,279
I’ll agree to any condition you give me.

631
00:40:53,280 --> 00:40:54,559
No.

632
00:40:54,560 --> 00:40:55,926
Don’t blame me for this.

633
00:40:58,160 --> 00:41:01,540
Let me down! I’m not going
to the secret ground!

634
00:41:03,000 --> 00:41:06,039
Let me go! I don’t want to
go there anymore!

635
00:41:06,040 --> 00:41:07,905
I don’t want to return to Mingxia Cave!

636
00:41:08,600 --> 00:41:10,239
- Open the entrance for me.
- Listen up.

637
00:41:10,240 --> 00:41:12,599
The entrance won’t be opened
unless I do it willingly.

638
00:41:12,600 --> 00:41:16,100
Are you saying that you can open it
if you do it willingly?

639
00:41:16,640 --> 00:41:19,665
That’s why you shouldn’t force me.
I won’t open the entrance for you.

640
00:41:19,666 --> 00:41:22,919
My father would lock me up
in Mingxia Cave forever if I do so.

641
00:41:22,920 --> 00:41:24,713
Ling Long and Sixth Senior
wouldn’t need to find Gudiao

642
00:41:24,714 --> 00:41:26,016
in order to obtain its horns then.

643
00:41:26,680 --> 00:41:28,599
You guys want to obtain Gudiao’s horns?

644
00:41:28,600 --> 00:41:29,922
Dream on.

645
00:41:30,640 --> 00:41:34,074
Although we’re not as
powerful as you, we can try.

646
00:41:36,280 --> 00:41:37,439
How about this?

647
00:41:37,440 --> 00:41:40,342
If I obtain Gudiao’s horns for you,

648
00:41:40,343 --> 00:41:42,123
you’ll bring me to the secret ground.

649
00:41:42,981 --> 00:41:44,273
Really?

650
00:41:44,274 --> 00:41:47,719
And I won’t let your father find out
that you sneak in.

651
00:41:47,720 --> 00:41:49,102
What do you think?

652
00:41:53,800 --> 00:41:55,751
That’s a deal.

653
00:41:59,880 --> 00:42:01,119
You!

654
00:42:01,120 --> 00:42:02,839
You don’t like it?

655
00:42:02,840 --> 00:42:04,399
I’ll wipe it off then.

656
00:42:04,400 --> 00:42:05,787
Get away from me!

657
00:42:25,920 --> 00:42:27,748
Yu Si Feng, we meet again.

658
00:42:30,600 --> 00:42:33,559
Why are you colder than
the rocks in Mingxia Cave?

659
00:42:33,560 --> 00:42:34,860
I’m not that familiar with you.

660
00:42:35,960 --> 00:42:37,559
Little Stammer?

661
00:42:37,560 --> 00:42:39,239
He hasn’t been a mute for a long time.

662
00:42:39,240 --> 00:42:42,380
Sixth Senior, can we fly together later?

663
00:42:43,849 --> 00:42:48,038
Xuan Ji, I have a stomachache.
I need to go to the loo.

664
00:42:48,039 --> 00:42:51,039
You can leave first.
I’ll catch up later.

665
00:42:51,040 --> 00:42:52,306
I...

666
00:42:54,800 --> 00:42:58,428
Little Stammer, can
we fly together later?

667
00:42:58,429 --> 00:42:59,908
My father and the rest are too fast.

668
00:42:59,909 --> 00:43:01,559
I’ll fall off when I fly with them.

669
00:43:01,560 --> 00:43:03,479
And he’ll scold me.

670
00:43:03,480 --> 00:43:06,463
No. I’m too fast for you.
And it is inappropriate as well.

671
00:43:08,320 --> 00:43:09,759
Xuan Ji.

672
00:43:09,760 --> 00:43:11,288
- Father.
- Where’s Min Yan?

673
00:43:13,320 --> 00:43:16,839
Sixth Senior said he was going to
the loo because of a stomachache.

674
00:43:16,840 --> 00:43:19,340
My goodness. You’ll fly with me later.

675
00:43:20,080 --> 00:43:21,839
I...

676
00:43:21,840 --> 00:43:24,700
Uncle, why don’t you let me
fly with Xuan Ji?

677
00:43:26,480 --> 00:43:29,222
Xuan Ji, don’t worry. I’ll fly slowly.

678
00:43:30,206 --> 00:43:31,616
It’s decided then.

679
00:43:41,320 --> 00:43:43,359
Little Six, why are you only here by now?

680
00:43:43,360 --> 00:43:45,039
I’ve been waiting for a long time.

681
00:43:45,040 --> 00:43:48,239
I’m bringing you along in secret.
We mustn’t let Master find out.

682
00:43:48,240 --> 00:43:49,552
Don’t worry.

683
00:44:19,960 --> 00:44:21,227
Is it fun?

684
00:44:22,160 --> 00:44:23,913
It’s my fault.

685
00:44:23,914 --> 00:44:26,160
I still don’t know how to fly
when I’m at this age.

686
00:44:26,161 --> 00:44:28,639
If not, I could fly by myself.

687
00:44:28,640 --> 00:44:31,445
- Senior Hao Chen, you can go faster.
- Okay.

688
00:44:31,446 --> 00:44:32,826
Okay.

689
00:44:32,827 --> 00:44:34,259
Brace yourself.
